name: Man, I Love Frenchies - Special Editions

metadata.name: The Year of the Frenchie - 2023
metadata.description: It's time to party like a Frenchie! Ring in 2023 with this adorable neon Frenchie! Painted in neon hues, this Frenchie is sure to put a smile on any face. The background is bursting with fireworks, representing the endless possibilities and excitement for what's in store for this year. So let's pop some champagne and raise a toast to a bright future. This one-of-a-kind piece is the must-have addition to any French bulldog lover's collection.
